topic.title: Libgen.io probably the best place to get books!
topic.body:
You should save this page, specially if you are an university student and need a certain textbook. The website is on the clearnet but I would recommend to get the books from the torrent link they offer and seed forever, because the mirrors are sometimes down or very slow.

Main link:

libgen.io

Alternative link:

gen.lib.rus.ec
